---
const shopUrl = 'https://butikk.percor.no';
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-bg-alt relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative element -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 lg:px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">

      <!-- Left: visual -->
      <div data-reveal="left" class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-primary rounded-2xl p-10 lg:p-14">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent/20 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-6">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent-light">Eksklusiv importør i Norge</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight mb-2">Payper</p>
              <p class="text-dark-text-secondary text-sm">Made in Italy — Since 1977</p>

              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-8">
                <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-accent-light">500+</p>
                  <p class="text-[11px] text-white/50 mt-1">Produkter</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-white">40+</p>
                  <p class="text-[11px] text-white/50 mt-1">År erfaring</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-accent-light">1</p>
                  <p class="text-[11px] text-white/50 mt-1">Norsk importør</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Floating badge -->
          <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 bg-accent text-white rounded-xl px-4 py-2 shadow-lg shadow-accent/30 rotate-3">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold">🇮🇹 Direkte fra Italia</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: story text -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <p data-reveal class="text-accent font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Vår stolthet</p>
        <h2 data-reveal class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-text leading-tight mb-6">
          Italiensk håndverk,<br />norsk service
        </h2>
        <div data-reveal class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            De fleste arbeidstøy-leverandører selger det samme fra de samme katalogene. Vi gjør det annerledes.
          </p>
          <p>
            Som <strong class="text-text">eneste norske importør av Payper</strong> har vi direkte tilgang til en av Europas ledende produsenter. Det betyr bedre priser, raskere levering, og produkter du ikke finner hos noen andre.
          </p>
          <p>
            Fra T-skjorter og pikéer til high-vis jakker og arbeidsbukser — alt designet i Italia, levert fra norsk lager.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8">
          <a href="/merkevarer/payper" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-primary-light transition-colors">
            Utforsk Payper
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href={shopUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-semibold hover:text-primary-light transition-colors">
            Se i nettbutikken
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7v10"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
